 conundrum: 'Inaccurate' materials used to teach Scottsdale students\"</a>. Jewish News of Greater Phoenix. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.jewishaz.com/issues/story.mv?051104+textbook\">the original</a> on 2012-06-09<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-11-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Curriculum+conundrum%3A+%27Inaccurate%27+materials+used+to+teach+Scottsdale+students&amp;rft.date=2005-11-04&amp;rft.aulast=Susser&amp;rft.aufirst=Deborah+Sussman&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jewishaz.com%2Fissues%2Fstory.mv%3F051104%2Btextbook&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+Alive%21+The+Medieval+World+and+Beyond\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Stilwell, Cinnamon (2008-06-11). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sfgate.com/politics/article/Islam-in-America-s-public-schools-Education-or-2482820.php\">\"Islam in America's public schools: Education or indoctrination?\"</a>. <i>San Francisco Chronicle</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-11-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=San+Francisco+Chronicle&amp;rft.atitle=Islam+in+America%27s+public+schools%3A+Education+or+indoctrination%3F&amp;rft.date=2008-06-11&amp;rft.aulast=Stilwell&amp;rft.aufirst=Cinnamon&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfgate.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2FIslam-in-America-s-public-schools-Education-or-2482820.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+Alive%21+The+Medieval+World+and+Beyond\" class=\"Z3988\"><s